	<div class="grid-article-bd">
		<h1 class="smart-dotdotdot">香菜，吃还是不吃，这是一种归属感</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-ft  clearfix">
		<span class="smart-date" data-originDate="2016-05-01 10:11:28 +0800"></span>
		<div class="ribbon">
				<span class="iconfont icon-message">16</span>
				<span class="iconfont icon-heart">53</span>
		</div>
